```plantuml
@startuml codahale_sneaker

actor User
participant "CLI (sneaker)" as CLI
participant "Manager" as Manager
participant "Envelope" as Envelope
participant "AWS KMS" as KMS
participant "AWS S3" as S3

User -> CLI : Execute command (e.g., upload secret)
CLI -> Manager : Forward request
Manager -> Envelope : Generate data key
Envelope -> KMS : GenerateDataKey()
KMS --> Envelope : Returns encrypted data key
Envelope -> Envelope : Encrypt secret (AES-256-GCM)
Envelope --> Manager : Returns encrypted secret + metadata
Manager -> S3 : Upload encrypted object
S3 --> Manager : Confirms upload
Manager --> CLI : Returns success
CLI --> User : Displays result

@enduml
```